#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Interal curve]

Given a #link("009S")[smooth vector field] $X$ for some #link("009D")[smooth manifold] $M$
and an initial point $x_0$ in $M$. Then an _integral curve_ through $x_0$ is a #link("009M")[curve]
$gamma: (-epsilon, epsilon) ->  M$ with
1. $gamma (0) =  x_0$ _"initial condition"_
2. $gamma'(t) =  X(gamma(t))$ for all $t in (-epsilon,epsilon)$ _"solution of the OdE is determined by the vector field"_
